## 10. Conclusion

This assignment helped me understand important web security concepts, especially through OWASP Top 10 and SQL basics. However, I also realized that I need more guidance and practice with hands-on security labs like WebGoat and PortSwigger. The difficulties I faced showed me that cybersecurity requires patience and step-by-step learning.

